headline: 3 Services Stocks in the Doghouse
summary: Business services providers thrive by solving complex operational challenges for their clients, allowing them to focus on their secret sauce. Furthermore, the demand for their offerings is rising as more clients outsource non-core functions, a trend that has enabled the industry to return 6.8% over the past six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 was up 3.6%.
